Guest User Stories
US-01: Register Account
Priority: High (MVP)
As a guest, I want to register an account so that I can borrow and lend items.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	Guests can enter their name, email, and password
•	Email must be unique
•	Account is created successfully

US-02: Login
Priority: High (MVP)
As a guest, I want to log in so that I can access my account and platform features.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	Guests can log in using valid credentials
•	Invalid credentials show an error message
•	Successful login redirects to home page

US-03: Browse Items
Priority: High (MVP)
As a guest, I want to browse available items so that I can see what items are available before registering.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	Guests can view a list of available items
•	Basic item details are visible
•	Borrowing requires a login

US-04: View Item Details
Priority: High (MVP)
As a guest or registered user, I want to view detailed information about an item so that I can decide whether to request it.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	Item details include description and availability
•	Item owner information is displayed

Registered User Stories
US-05: Create Item Listing
Priority: High (MVP)
As a registered user, I want to create an item listing so that others can borrow my item.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	User enters item title, description, category, and availability
•	Listing is saved successfully
•	Listing appears in browse items

US-06: Request to Borrow Item
Priority: High (MVP)
As a registered user, I want to request to borrow an item so that I can use it for a specific time period.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	User selects borrow start and end dates
•	User cannot request their own item
•	Request status is set to “Pending.”

US-07: View Borrow Request Status
Priority: High (MVP)
As a registered user, I want to view the status of my borrow requests so that I know whether they are approved or pending.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	User can view request status
•	Status updates when approved or rejected

US-08: Approve or Reject Borrow Request
Priority: High (MVP)
As an item owner, I want to approve or reject borrow requests so that I can control who borrows my item.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	Owner can view incoming requests
•	Owner can approve or reject a request
•	Request status updates correctly

US-09: View Pickup Details
Priority: Medium (MVP)
As a borrower, I want to view confirmed pickup details so that I know when and where to collect the item.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	Pickup details are visible only after approval
•	Details are agreed through in-app messaging

US-10: In-App Messaging
Priority: Medium (MVP)
As a registered user, I want to message another user so that pickup details can be discussed safely.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	Messaging is enabled after request approval
•	Messages remain within the platform

US-11: Report User or Listing
Priority: Medium
As a registered user, I want to report a user or listing so that unsafe behaviour can be reviewed.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	User can submit a report with a reason
•	Report is stored for admin review

Admin User Stories
US-12: Admin Login
Priority: Medium
As an admin, I want to log in so that I can manage the platform securely.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	Admin login requires valid credentials
•	Admin-only access is enforced

US-13: Review Reports
Priority: Medium
As an admin, I want to review reported users or listings so that appropriate moderation action can be taken.
Acceptance Criteria:
•	Admin can view submitted reports
•	Admin can take action on reports
